      1. ^ a b c The European Union (EU) is an economic và political union of Bản mẫu:EUnum member states that are located primarily in Europe. The EU is included as a separate entity in The World Factbook of CIA because it has many attributes of independent nations, being much more than a free-trade association such as ASEAN, NAFTA, or Mercosur.[4]As the EU is not a country, India is the third ranked country on these lists.
